metadata.name: The 14th Floor
metadata.description:
They've always wanted to kick us out
some feared this place
some of them used to call the police all the time
the roof leaked
the rent was high
but not high enough to get a nice service
they didn't talk to us in the hallways
some people used to complain about the noises
even when the apartments were empty
some of them wanted to steal our cat
this place was so inspiring
it was the last floor
someone tried to set fire to the building once
some of them used to fight in the stairs 
and then have sex in the elevator
some of them hated this place
but all of them wanted to live in the 14th floor
and you will too.
